The paper discusses the development of a machine learning-based metasystem for question answering over RDF data, which involves techniques from artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of existing systems also suggests a focus on database systems (cs.DB).
